{"tid":2188651,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國小麥進口料創逾20年高","createTime":"2020-09-04T11:09:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T11:09:57.000Z","uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"691af4886242ca7d828b4a1bf7c7f42ab53d7fbd","tid":2188651,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T11:09:57.000Z","msg":"國家糧油訊息中心最新預估顯示，中國在6月份開始的年度料將進口700萬噸小麥，較此前的預估上調100萬噸。<br />\n<br />\n根據美國農業部數據，這是1995至1996年度以來的最高水平。<br />\n<br />\n中國在上一個銷售年度進口420萬噸小麥。除糧食消費外，由於玉米價格較高，小麥還被用作玉米的替代品。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/china/article/2574831\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fchina%2Farticle%2F2574831&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1ccLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=19689ab2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/china/article/2574831</a>"}]}